    .experience-types
        .experience-type
            i.fa.fa-cogs.fa-5x.experience-type-icon
            h2.experience-type-title Methodology
            p.experience-type-describe Experience with Agile methodologies like XP and Scrum. I use these methodologies to promote effective interaction between team members to deliver value to the business.

        .experience-type
            i.fa.fa-code.fa-5x.experience-type-icon
            h2.experience-type-title Code
            p.experience-type-describe Regardless of the code I'm using I like to write code following best practices and always trying to solve problems in the most performative way. In backend I'm Java certifited and I like develop in languages such as Ruby and golang. In the frontend I like to work with preprocessors in CSS and JavaScript with its awesome frameworks.

        .experience-type
            i.fa.fa-flask.fa-5x.experience-type-icon
            h2.experience-type-title User Experience
            p.experience-type-describe In UX exploring many different approaches to solving a specific user problem and ensure that the product logically flows from one step to the next. I like to do this conducting in-person user tests to observe one's behavior and identifying verval and non-verbal stumbling blocks, they refine and iterate to create the "best" user experience.
